events.1610: Antananarivo founded as capital of the Merina Kingdom by Andrianjaka
events.1710: Capital of Merina Kingdom relocated to Ambohimanga from Antananarivo by Andriantsimitoviaminandriandrazaka
events.1794: Capital of Merina Kingdom relocated to Antananarivo from Ambohimanga by Andrianampoinimerina
events.1840: Manjakamiadana built in the Rova of Antananarivo (palace)
events.1895: City besieged and captured by French forces during the Second Madagascar expedition
events.1925: Botanical and Zoological Garden of Tsimbazaza founded
events.1960: City becomes capital of the new Malagasy Republic
events.1972: Political unrest; city hall burns down
events.1995: November: Rova of Antananarivo burns down
events.1997: 1997 Jeux de la Francophonie held in Antananarivo
events.2016: November: Meeting of the Organisation internationale de la Francophonie held in city
